    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "In addition to wakuext_contacts, `wakuext_markAllRead` is also called when switching channels, and is causing part of the slowdown due to the UPDATE statement being used.  Some possible improvements are to either call `wakuext_markMessagesSeen`  with the specific message Ids, or call `wakuext_markAllRead` async.  In addition to this, add an index over the `local_chat_id` column of `user_messages` table, but with regards to this @jrainville suggest to discuss with Mobile team due to concerns related to storage size",
